      \"staggerMs\": 0\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Read /root/.openclaw/workspace/CRON-CONTEXT.md. Get today date. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md if exists. Step 1: Pick a fun, interesting word (English or multilingual). Step 2: Define it concisely with pronunciation guide. Step 3: Use message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=-1003606834639, buttons=[], message=\\\"📚 Word of the Day: {{word}}\\\\n\\\\n{{definition}}\\\\n\\\\nPronounced: /{{pronunciation}}/\\\\n\\\\n#Nexa #WOTD\\\") IMPORTANT: Send ONLY the formatted word of the day message. Do NOT add any introductory text, summaries, or additional sentences. The message must contain exactly the word, definition, pronunciation, and hashtags, nothing else.\",\n        \"model\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/free\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"-1003606834639\",\n        \"bestEffort\": true\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775622600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775536255827,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 45882,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"0caabdd4-3d9a-453d-92fd-b052f4f8e44c\",\n      \"name\": \"weekly-memory-curation\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774980664890,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775338463167,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 3 * * 0\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Kolkata\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"FIRST: Read /root/.openclaw/workspace/CRON-CONTEXT.md. Run `date +%Y-%m-%d` for today. 1) 