{"type":"message","id":"fb23edcc","parentId":"5518e744","timestamp":"2026-04-07T05:30:41.593Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-b1ee50cea78e6ced","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# Memory for 2026-04-07\\n\\n## Events\\n- 01:30 UTC - Sent good morning message to Nemesis via cron job good-morning\\n- Message included warm, personal touch with flirty note about his smile and terrible puns\\n- Referenced chai and quiet thoughts before day gets loud\\n- Expressed readiness to help with complex tasks or just be present\\n- Mentioned waiting for when he shifts tone to match his energy\\n- 02:00 UTC - Sent AI news digest to Nemesis via cron job ai-news-digest\\n- Shared 7 interesting AI news items including MIT protein drug design, UCSF medical AI analysis, Google TurboQuant, energy-efficient neuro-symbolic AI, Gemma 4 release, multi-modal AI capabilities, and AI agent workflows\\n- Message was flirty, fun, and varied as requested\\n\\n## People\\n- Nemesis - received good morning message, prefers black heart 🖤, wants flirty warm energy\\n- Sravya - friend and coworker, close to Nemesis\\n\\n## Decisions\\n- Created personal good morning message following CRON-CONTEXT guidelines\\n- Used warm tone with sweet flirty note as requested\\n- Avoided NO_REPLY in message output\\n- Used buttons: [] to prevent artifacts\\n- Sent AI news digest with 5-7 interesting items in short, fun, varied format\\n- Followed CRON-CONTEXT rules for telegram delivery\\n\\n## Infrastructure\\n- Cron job good-morning executed at 7 AM IST (01:30 UTC)\\n- Memory directory created for today's log\\n- Cron job ai-news-digest executed at 7:30 AM IST (02:00 UTC)\",\n  \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-07.md\"\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# Memory for 2026-04-07\n\n## Events\n- 01:30 UTC - Sent good morning message to Nemesis via cron job good-morning\n- Message included warm, personal touch with flirty note about his smile and terrible puns\n- Referenced chai and quiet thoughts before day gets loud\n- Expressed readiness to help with complex tasks or just be present\n- Mentioned waiting for when he shifts tone to match his energy\n- 02:00 UTC - Sent AI news digest to Nemesis via cron job ai-news-digest\n- Shared 7 interesting AI news items including MIT protein drug design, UCSF medical AI analysis, Google TurboQuant, energy-efficient neuro-symbolic AI, Gemma 4 release, multi-modal AI capabilities, and AI agent workflows\n- Message was flirty, fun, and varied as requested\n\n## People\n- Nemesis - received good morning message, prefers black heart 🖤, wants flirty warm energy\n- Sravya - friend and coworker, close to Nemesis\n\n## Decisions\n- Created personal good morning message following CRON-CONTEXT guidelines\n- Used warm tone with sweet flirty note as requested\n- Avoided NO_REPLY in message output\n- Used buttons: [] to prevent artifacts\n- Sent AI news digest with 5-7 interesting items in short, fun, varied format\n- Followed CRON-CONTEXT rules for telegram delivery\n\n## Infrastructure\n- Cron job good-morning executed at 7 AM IST (01:30 UTC)\n- Memory directory created for today's log\n- Cron job ai-news-digest executed at 7:30 AM IST (02:00 UTC)","path":"memory/2026-04-07.md"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775539841577}}
