istory again. Let me wait 30 seconds and then check. Actually, I can check the cron jobs list again to see if the temporary job is still there or if it ran. Since it's not in the list, it likely ran and was deleted. Let me check the session history for any new messages that might have come from that job. Let me get the session history and look for any messages that might contain war update information. Let me also check if there are any new files in the workspace that might contain output. Actually, let me just check the session history one more time and see if there are any new messages. Let me also check if the user has received any message via Telegram (though I can't see that directly). Let me get the session history and look for any messages from the agent or system that might contain the war update. Let me do that now.\\n\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"chatcmpl-tool-a46362bbc348f92f\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_history\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:7924461837\",\n            \"limit\": 30\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"kilocode\",\n      \"model\": \"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775539861001,\n      \"responseId\": \"gen-1775539861-sTLDMkxmGnCfwc9O5rKr\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"ab2cd6d4\",\n        \"seq\": 35\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Let me check for any new messages in the session that might contain the war update output. Let me look at the most recent messages in the session history.\\n\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"chatcmpl-tool-ab8876dc8557c6cb\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_history\",\n          \"arguments\