n to see if the temporary execution job is still there or if it ran recently. I'll also check if there are any error statuses.\n\nLet me get the current cron jobs list.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-af3338fc2c448c01","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":76070,"output":950,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77020,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775540136967,"responseId":"gen-1775540137-zMsrGj0agqJraJuV2H5j"}}
