{"type":"message","id":"2701073e","parentId":"710dd5fe","timestamp":"2026-04-07T05:38:54.277Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-894b02f416b2b945","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a9ae0666-64da-4949-b49a-b14025084015\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-war-update-execution\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775540315804,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775540315804,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-04-07T05:39:05.724Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Today's date is 2026-04-07. \\n\\nPlease provide a comprehensive global war and conflict update for Nemesis with the following structure:\\n\\n**Historical Context (approximately 100 words, excluding the 24hr update):**\\n- Overview of major ongoing global conflicts and tensions\\n- Focus on Iran-US situation as requested\\n- Include other significant conflicts worldwide\\n- Brief context on how situations have evolved to current state\\n\\n**Last 24 Hours Developments:**\\n- Key events and developments in the last 24 hours\\n- Specific updates on Iran-US tensions\\n- Other significant conflict zone updates\\n- Any diplomatic initiatives or escalations\\n\\n**India-Specific Implications:**\\n- How these conflicts affect India's interests\\n- Predictions for future impact on India based on current trends\\n- India's potential role or stance in these situations\\n\\n**Important Instructions:**\\n- Cross-verify information using multiple sources before presenting facts\\n- Keep the historical summary to approximately 100 words (not including the 24hr update section)\\n- Be concise but comprehensive\\n- Use clear, accessible language\\n- If uncertain about any information, state the uncertainty rather than guessing\\n- Format the response clearly with the section headers as shown above\\n\\nPlease execute this request using your available tools (including web search for verification) and send the result to Nemesis via Telegram message.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775540345724\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"eeef1692-7e97-45f3-ad50-814f0afcae29\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:7924461837\",\n      \"name\": \"heartbeat-health-monitor\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775415426580,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775538128712,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 * * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"UTC\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run: cd /root/.openclaw/workspace && OUTPUT=$(python3 scripts/heartbeat_health_cron.py 2>&1); EXIT_CODE=$?; if [ $EXIT_CODE -eq 2 ]; then ALERT_MSG=$(echo \\\"$OUTPUT\\\" | grep '^ALERT_MESSAGE::' | sed 's/^ALERT_MESSAGE:://'); if [ -n \\\"$ALERT_MSG\\\" ]; then message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=7924461837, message=\\\"$ALERT_MSG\\\"); else echo \\\"Failed to extract alert message from output: $OUTPUT\\\"; fi; else echo \\\"Heartbeat health check completed with exit code $EXIT_CODE\\\"; fi\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"7924461837\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775541638099,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775538038107,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 90605,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"feee69f8-6016-4f8f-a09c-08b39d9a9191\",\n      \"name\": \"github-backup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774980647416,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775539404420,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */2 * * *\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run these commands: cd /root/.openclaw/workspace && git add -A && git diff --cached --quiet && echo \\\"nothing to commit\\\" || (git commit -m \\\"auto backup\\\" && git push). Report result to Nemesis via message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=7924461837) only if there was an error. If nothing changed, reply NO_REPLY.\",\n        \"model\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/free\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775541680664,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775539373459,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 30961,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"708c7b32-b32f-40d5-9cc3-34c519f4e55c\",\n      \"name\": \"cron-health-monitor\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774878027010,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775522038461,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Kolkata\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the cron health check script: python3 /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/cron-health-check/scripts/check_cron_health.py. If any jobs show warning or critical status, 