ist all memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md files. 2) For files older than 30 days, read them, extract anything worth keeping, add to MEMORY.md, then delete the old file. 3) Clean up MEMORY.md — remove stale/outdated entries, keep it under 50 lines. 4) Push to GitHub. 5) Message Nemesis at target=7924461837 with summary of what was cleaned.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775943000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775338371927,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 91240,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ac311486-d2d0-4fad-ac7f-ae54a2649bb0\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:group:-1003606834639\",\n      \"name\": \"April 27 exam reminder (good morning)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775322392409,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775322392409,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 27 4 *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Kolkata\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Read /root/.openclaw/workspace/CRON-CONTEXT.md. Send the following exact message to the Nrexya group using message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=-1003606834639): '🌅 Good morning, Nrexya! \\\\n\\\\nToday is April 27 — exam day! Wishing everyone the best, especially those with exams. You've prepared well, go crush it! 💪\\\\n\\\\nHave a great Saturday! 🖤'\",\n        \"model\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/free\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777257000000\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 14,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\