repeated requests in the group, which means they're coming from my responses here. I'll make sure my future responses in this DM session don't create that echo effect in the group.\n\nIs there a specific timeframe or topic from the group chat you'd like me to focus on, or would you prefer I just monitor and respond appropriately without trying to fetch history unless you specifically need something from the past?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":118958,"output":659,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119617,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775548159397,"responseId":"gen-1775548160-Q1Ha4QxEIqk7zIGkN1HC"}}
