{"type":"message","id":"25008198","parentId":"3e2bfb62","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:51:15.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, I need to check what personal messages I've actually sent in the group chat. Let me look at the group messages to see what I've been sending there.\n\nActually, I should first check if I can access the group messages properly. Let me try to get the group message history again, but this time I'll be careful not to echo the request back.\n\nFrom the conversation, it seems like I've been sending personal messages in the group that I shouldn't be sending. Let me check what those messages are.\n\nLet me try to access the group session history properly this time, and if I can't, I'll explain what I can see from my memory logs and recent activity.\n\nActually, let me first check the group messages by trying to access the session history for the group chat. If I get a permission error, I'll handle it appropriately.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-beb54caee9b1890e","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:telegram:group:-1003606834639","limit":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":105395,"output":444,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775548255122,"responseId":"gen-1775548256-KqHf89hz6pCqNxdf70Zs"}}
